c: 9
v: 36
t: "Tabitii limoore lebbi …óin ka Alla, ko lebbi sappo e …ói…ói, ka Alluwal Alla (reenaangal), √Ďalnde O tagunoo kammuuli …óin e leydi ndin. No e majji nayi hormanteeji : Ko …óum woni diina √Īii…ďuka. Wata on too√Īu e majji wonkiiji mon. Ha…ďee sirkoo…ďe fow ma…ď…ďe wano …ďe ha…ďirta on …ďe fow ma…ď…ďe. Anndon pellet, Alla na wondi e gom…óum…ďe …ďen"